com.kinvey
Interface KinveyUser

All Known Implementing Classes:
KinveyUserImpl
public interface KinveyUser

Kinvey provides a user service to manage the users of your application and to provide user based access controls to the data stored with Kinvey.

To make life simple for you, if you don’t wish to have named users, this library will manage them for you.

Automatically generated users are tied to the device they’re created on, therefore provide default device based access controls.
